## 2. Data Collection

Flamix may collect limited data to function properly. This may include:

- Guild (server) ID
- Channel ID
- User ID
- Messages (for command processing only)

**Flamix does not store message content unless explicitly stated in a feature description.**

Data is only used to improve and operate the Bot. We do not sell, share, or expose your data to third parties.

